OL,7,FA mother has written to King Charles,
OL,8,Fasking him to support her campaign for
OL,9,Ftougher sentences for people who fail
OL,10,Fto stop at the scene of an incident,
OL,11,Fafter her son was killed in a hit and
OL,12,Frun.
OL,14,FWilliam Brown, 7, was retrieving his
OL,15,Ffootball from the coast road at
OL,16,FSandgate, Folkestone in Kent on 6
OL,17,FDecember 2023, when he was struck by a
OL,18,Fvan driven. He died at the scene.
