OL,7,FWilliam's mother, Laura Brown wants
OL,8,Fharsher punishments for those who
OL,9,Fleave the scene of a collision.
OL,11,FThe court imposed an immediate driving
OL,12,Fban, and he will be sentenced on 7
OL,13,FJuly. As it is a summary offence, the
OL,14,Fcurrent maximum sentence is six months.
OL,16,FLaura Brown has received 8,000
OL,17,Fsignatures on her petition, Justice
OL,18,FFor All Hit-And-Run Victims.
