OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian, Laura Brown
OL,8,Fsaid: "Once people realise the
OL,9,Fsentencing you can get from what's
OL,10,Fhappened to William, they'll be
OL,11,Fshocked.
OL,13,F"Hopefully (the King) will feel the
OL,14,Fsame and will want to make a change."
OL,16,FThe King had intervened, granting
OL,17,Fpermission for an ancient churchyard
OL,18,Fin Folkestone to be reopened, so
OL,19,FWilliam could be buried there, after
OL,20,Fhis parents wrote a letter about their
OL,21,Frequest.
